PerlIO::via::SeqIO - PerlIO layer for biological sequence data

PerlIO::via::SeqIO is a layer using the BioPerl (http://bioperl.org)
toolkit for reading and writing flat sequence formats (such as fasta
or embl) using magic filehandles and our old friends <> and print.

BioPerl will need to be installed before use.  See
http://bioperl.org/Installation.

Thanks for downloading!

To install, simply:

perl Build.PL
./Build
./Build test
./Build install

